# 🎨 CSS Types Demonstration Project

## 📌 Description
This project demonstrates the use of:
- Inline CSS
- Internal CSS
- External CSS  

It also includes a gallery of 5 centered images using containers.

---

## 🚀 Features
- Inline CSS (used inside HTML elements)
- Internal CSS (inside `<style>` tag)
- External CSS (linked `.css` file)
- 5 image containers
- Centered layout using Flexbox
- Organized project structure

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used
- HTML
- CSS

